widgets_values: The image shows a young woman sitting on the steps of a blue door. She is wearing a beige trench coat, beige pants, and white sneakers. She has long dark hair and is resting her chin on her hand. The door is painted blue and has a metal gate on the left side. The background is a gray wall with a red pipe running along it. The woman is looking off to the side with a thoughtful expression on her face.
